# ITI-41 provide and register document set api call

### ITI-41: Provide and Register Document Set-b

ITI-41 is used to transmit a set of documents and associated metadata

When receiving the request the Repository:

1. Validates the received data
2. Adds the computed data
3. Store the received document and the meta-data
